casebody.data:
Friday, March 25, 1994

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-808. Horner v. Toledo Hosp.

Lucas County, No. L-91-417. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal and a cross-appeal from the Court of Appeals for Lucas County. Upon consideration of appellee/cross-appellant’s application to dismiss her cross-appeal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the cross-appeal be, and the same is hereby, dismissed, effective March 23, 1994.
